refentry.refsect1:
    &ref.title.attributes;


      Attributes for ZipTask

      &taskAttributes.table.titlesLine.all;



        destfile

        String

        .ZIP filename

        &attributes.defaultValue.NA;

        &attributes.required.yes;




        basedir

        String

        Base directory to zip (if no fileset
        specified, entire directory contents will be included in the
        archive)

        &attributes.defaultValue.NA;

        &attributes.required.no;




        prefix

        String

        File path prefix to use when adding files to
        zip

        &attributes.defaultValue.NA;

        &attributes.required.no;




        includeemptydirs

        Boolean

        If set to true, also empty
        directories are copied.

        true

        &attributes.required.no;




Important note: using
    basedir and <fileset>
    simultaneously can result in strange contents in the archive.
